{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 44,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الدُّخَانِ",
    "englishName": "Ad-Dukhaan",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Smoke",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 59,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4415,
        "text": "哈一，米目。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4416,
        "text": "以明确的经典盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4417,
        "text": "在一个吉祥的夜间，我确已降示它，我确是警告者。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4418,
        "text": "在那夜里，一切睿智的事，都被判定，",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4419,
        "text": "那是按照从我那里了出的命令的。我确是派遣使者的。",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4420,
        "text": "那是由于从你的主发出的恩惠。他确是全聪的，确是全知的。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4421,
        "text": "他是天地万物的主，如果你们是坚信者。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4422,
        "text": "除他外，绝无应受崇拜的。他能使死者生，能使生者死，他是你们的主，也是你们祖先的主。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4423,
        "text": "不然，他们是在疑惑中的，是游戏的。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4424,
        "text": "你应当等待烟雾漫天的日子，",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4425,
        "text": "那烟雾将笼罩世人，他们说：这是一种痛苦的刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4426,
        "text": "我们的主啊！求你为我们解除这种刑罚，我们确是信道的。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4427,
        "text": "他们怎能觉悟呢？显赫的使者，确已来临他们，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4428,
        "text": "而他们却鄙弃他。他们说：他是受教的，是疯狂的。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4429,
        "text": "我必定要暂时解除这种刑罚，你们必定复返于悖逆。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4430,
        "text": "我进行最大的袭击之日，我必定要惩罚他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4431,
        "text": "在他们之前，我确已考验了法老的百姓。有一个高贵的使者来临他们，",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4432,
        "text": "说：你们把真主的仆人们交给我吧！我确是一个忠实的使者，奉命来教化你们的。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4433,
        "text": "你们不要对真主高傲。我必定要昭示你们一个明证。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4434,
        "text": "我确已求庇于我的主和你们的主，免遭你们的谋害。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4435,
        "text": "如果你们不归信我，那末，你们放任我吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4436,
        "text": "他就祈祷他的主说：这等人，确是犯罪的民众。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4437,
        "text": "（主说）：你带着我的众仆在夜间出走吧！你们必定要被追赶。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4438,
        "text": "你让海水保持平静，他们必定是被淹死的军队。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4439,
        "text": "他们曾抛下若干园圃和泉源，",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4440,
        "text": "庄稼和美宅，",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4441,
        "text": "以及他们所享受的福泽！",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4442,
        "text": "结局是这样的：我曾使别的民众继承他们，",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4443,
        "text": "天地没有哭他们，他们也没有获得缓刑。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4444,
        "text": "我确已使以色列的后裔摆脱了凌辱的刑罚--",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4445,
        "text": "法老的刑罚。他确是高傲的，确是过分的。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4446,
        "text": "我确已本真知而选拔他们，使他们超轶各民族，",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4447,
        "text": "我赏赐他们许多迹象，都是有明显的试验的。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4448,
        "text": "这等人必定要说：",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4449,
        "text": "我们只有初次的死亡，我们不会复活。",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4450,
        "text": "你们把我们的祖先召唤回来吧，如果你们是说实话的。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4451,
        "text": "他们是更高贵的呢？还是图白的宗族是更高贵呢？在他们之前的许多民族，我已加以毁灭了；因为他们确是犯罪者。",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4452,
        "text": "我没有以游戏的态度创造天地万物，",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4453,
        "text": "我只本真理而创造之，但他们大半不知道。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4454,
        "text": "甄别日，确是为他们全体预定的日期。",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4455,
        "text": "在那日，朋友对于朋友，毫无裨益，他们也不蒙援助；",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4456,
        "text": "惟真主所怜恤者则不然。他确是万能的，确是至慈的。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4457,
        "text": "櫕（木+苦）木的果实，",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4458,
        "text": "确是罪人的食品，",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4459,
        "text": "象油脚样在他们的腹中沸腾，",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4460,
        "text": "象开水一样地沸腾。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4461,
        "text": "（主说）你们捉住他，然后，把他拖入火狱中，",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4462,
        "text": "然后，再把沸水的刑罚倾注在他的头上！",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4463,
        "text": "你尝试吧！你确是显赫的，确是尊贵的！",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4464,
        "text": "这（刑罚）确是你们生前所怀疑的。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4465,
        "text": "敬畏者必定要住在安全的地方--",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4466,
        "text": "住在乐园之中，住在泉源之滨，",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4467,
        "text": "穿着绫罗绸缎，相向而坐。",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4468,
        "text": "结局是这样的：我将以白皙的、美目的女子，做他们的伴侣。",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4469,
        "text": "他们在乐园中，将安全地索取各种水果。",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4470,
        "text": "他们在乐园中，除初次死亡外不再尝死的滋味。真主将使他们得免于火狱的刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4471,
        "text": "那是由于你的主的恩典，那确是伟大的成功。",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4472,
        "text": "我以你的语言，使《古兰经》成为易解的，只为希望他们能觉悟。",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4473,
        "text": "你等待吧，他们确是等待着的！",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
